             were indicted for <rs id="t18320906-317-off1791" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320906-317-off1791" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320906-317-off1791" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320906-317-cd1792" type="crimeDate">12th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-317-off1791 t18320906-317-cd1792"></join>, 1 jar, value 4d.; 36 pennies, and 84 halfpence, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-317-victim2612" type="victimName">
                           Leonard 
                           Wass
                        <interp inst="t18320906-317-victim2612" type="surname" value="Wass"></interp>
